g.title: j1762084113
g.text: u've told me so many awful stories about the Orokin... was there ever anyone who turned their back on their way of life?

g.title: j3381942086
g.text: Believe it or not, Doctor Albrecht Entrati.

g.title: j1350863733
g.text: Most of them ended up dead. But Albrecht Entrati did, in his own way.

g.title: j3037245898
g.text: ew.

g.title: j885702284
g.text: ugh, that guy. always slipping through death's grip.

g.title: j3411955454
g.text: and here I was hoping it’d be someone... cooler.

g.title: j2028215871
g.text: Sorry to disappoint. He’s your guy. Refused Kuva, which allows them to be immortal. Didn’t go for the fashionable long arm. None of it.

g.title: j3879876289
g.text: Yeah um... I'll think of a cool Orokin. Give me a minute.

g.title: j1340669235
g.text: only to chase after whatever served him best, I’m sure.

g.title: j1158386011
g.text: well, there's u, I guess ^_^

g.title: j4284382221
g.text: Did you ever respect Entrati?

g.title: j251709330
g.text: What do you really think of Entrati? Beyond the “uncool” verdict.

g.title: j2503518390
g.text: Hah. I'm not an Orokin. I'm just from their empire. Very different.

g.title: j2045144683
g.text: hmm. pulling out the big questions now, huh? I guess u’ve earned it.

g.title: j3135122991
g.text: I have no respect left to lose for the guy ^_^

g.title: j1032519075
g.text: ooooh. confusing

g.title: j1329105806
g.text: people like him only pretend to be charming when it serves them

g.title: j1767772328
g.text: i really didn't like entrati, though. people like him only pretend to be charming when it serves them

g.title: j192373220
g.text: What do you think he's really after?

g.title: j2876493172
g.text: So you found him charming at some point.

g.title: j2160992398
g.text: control. complete domination.

g.title: j1384841905
g.text: i wouldn’t go that far. more like I was open to respecting him.

g.title: j340364828
g.text: not in the fun, pop star world-tour way either.

g.title: j1576633586
g.text: but he threw that away.

g.title: j3579988902
g.text: he devours whatever he touches. not even the whole universe would be enough for him.

g.title: j979663618
g.text: And you knew that early on? You’re the most intuitive in the Hex. If anyone would’ve had a gut feeling, it’d be you.

g.title: j4203194027
g.text: I'm inclined to agree with you.

g.title: j3017123048
g.text: I don't know. There's an awful lot of universe out there. :P

g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j3539081043
g.text: but he'd try and that's the problem

g.title: j2614569743
g.text: thank you. ^_^

g.title: j1502511139
g.text: not right away, but pretty early, I got this sinking feeling like something bad was about to happen every time he was nice

g.title: j4249918031
g.text: and back then, I didn’t have the words for it, but it always felt like HE would be the one behind whatever went wrong.

g.title: j3547168984
g.text: but when he has everyone around u fooled, what can u really do?

g.title: j3000683414
g.text: Do you think he actually had everyone fooled?

g.title: j1850244852
g.text: I guess you wait for them to see it for themselves.

g.title: j2225610169
g.text: well, maybe not

g.title: j1328660927
g.text: ya

g.title: j1023290907
g.text: more like everyone was too scared to challenge him

g.title: j150310853
g.text: it’s kinda my curse, instinctively playing nice

g.title: j4204689566
g.text: which annoys me to no end.

g.title: j1669961276
g.text: maybe if I’d said something, more people would’ve seen through him sooner.

g.title: j1208643694
g.text: If it’s any comfort, he’s had the same effect where I’m from too.

g.title: j4174436639
g.text: You’re not alone there. He left his mark on everyone.

g.title: j3623296376
g.text: that’s... bittersweet, I guess.

g.title: j3844777065
g.text: ugh. not even the future is safe from that guy.

g.title: j133085080
g.text: He left behind a daughter who’s still trying to fix the pieces he shattered. Angry as she is, I feel like she can't help believing in him.

g.title: j693430258
g.text: Yeah. He left behind his lover to mend the damage he did to countless people... and animals.

g.title: j2425177920
g.text: that's just him. that's what he does.

g.title: j937877074
g.text: he's the only being of emptiness I've ever known.

g.title: j485407584
g.text: when he finds something he wants, he consumes it completely, then tosses it away when it's spent. always in the most heartless, self-serving way.

g.title: j3631307505
g.text: Yeah... “uncool” is starting to sound like an understatement.

g.title: j2675384871
g.text: Damn. Hey, don't hold back.

g.title: j1862615062
g.text: I doubt even the people who like him would deny that.

g.title: j1310497439

g.text: LOL I've never met anyone less cool!

g.title: j3121931525

g.title: j3555668269

g.text: and every day, I see small acts of defiance from an old, forgotten mall in Höllvania that remind me the human spirit is unbreakable

g.text: Hmm. If nothing else, your perspective alone proves the human spirit really can’t be broken.
